data.name: 0000 (388.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Anyway, #W20Haruhi should be satisfied with that, right?

data.name: 0001 (388.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: It's unfortunate but, I don't think it'll go so smoothly.

data.name: 0002 (388.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What do you mean, Koizumi…？

data.name: 0003 (388.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Well, please think about it for a moment.

data.name: 0004 (388.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Of the mysterious phenomena the Computer Society encountered, three more remain.

data.name: 0006 (388.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Considering this is Miss Suzumiya, I somehow doubt it'll be so easy.

data.name: 0007 (388.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Damn it. There's no reason to contest anything Koizumi said.

data.name: 0008 (388.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Instead, my seasoned intuition is giving me a stern warning—

data.name: 0009 (388.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: "This is just the beginning."

data.name: 0010 (388.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …Nagato, I just want to make sure of one thing.

data.name: 0012 (388.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: What?

data.name: 0013 (388.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: That so-called data lifeform—are there any others?

data.name: 0014 (388.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: They exist.

data.name: 0015 (388.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Currently, the confirmable population is—

data.name: 0016 (388.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: H-hold on! You don't have to say it!

data.name: 0017 (388.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I was dangerously close to hearing something I didn't want to know.

data.name: 0018 (388.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: This is my personal opinion but, if we're done after only three,#W30 I'd rather do more.

data.name: 0019 (388.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Huh…?!

data.name: 0022 (388.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: How long are you gonna make me wait, Kyon?!

data.name: 0023 (388.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Haruhi…

data.name: 0024 (388.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: And I'll tell you what,#W20 I'm not happy with this at all!

data.name: 0025 (388.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: To begin with, what I want is a mystery worthy of the new seven wonders.

data.name: 0026 (388.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: If this ends up like some third rate mystery, I'd rather not have a mystery at all!

data.name: 0027 (388.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Got that? If so, get moving now!

data.name: 0028 (388.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: What a mess…

data.name: 0029 (388.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: This Haruhi… Far from being satisfied, she's getting even more fired up instead.

data.name: 0030 (388.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Koizumi—what's next?

data.name: 0031 (388.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Of course, Miss Suzumiya.

data.name: 0032 (388.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Chronologically—the case of the piano in the music room. Isn't that perfect?

data.name: 0033 (388.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Then let's go for that!

data.name: 0034 (388.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: This time, I'll gaze upon real unnatural phenomena with my own eyes!

data.name: 0035 (388.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: About Haruhi.
